				<h5>Uses of Personal Information</h5>
				<p>Leema functions as a marketplace that allows users who comply with Leema’s policies to offer, sell and purchase goods at a specified price. The personally identifiable information you choose to provide on our website is used to help you operate within the marketplace. Other information that does not personally identify you as an individual is collected by Leema from Users (such as, for example, patterns of utilization) and is exclusively owned by Leema. This information can be utilized by Leema in such manner as Leema, in its sole discretion, deems appropriate.</p>
